metadata.name: LFGKIDS_GA#1/4
metadata.description:
LFGKIDS_GA collection is a genesis edition of LFGKIDS art with 1 NFT and limited physical copies with artist signature.

LFGKIDS_GA #1 physical copies were shipped to:

/1 NAP Coffee, AS, Guizhou, China
/2 SIDELOOK Studio, GY, Guizhou, China
/3 Wang Xiao Xue, China
/4 HUKAKA Cooking, GY, Guizhou, China
